{"tid":2263082,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"上海地鐵 12 月 1 日起禁手機「外放聲音」","createTime":"2020-10-29T15:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T15:09:44.000Z","uid":379538,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5519ec4f6514e6f2baa3f56780d6b0b6a67efe97","tid":2263082,"uid":379538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"來自《澎湃新聞》 的報導指近日上海地鐵車廂內貼出「使用電子設備時禁止外放聲音」的標識。據上海交通委官網公開信息顯示，12 月 1 日起會實施新修訂的《上海市軌道交通乘客守則》，當中會禁止手機外放聲音。<br />\n<br />\n外放聲音主要是用手機播放影片、語音訊息、玩手機遊戲造成，而手機發出的聲音成為了車箱環境變得嘈雜的主要原因。<br />\n<br />\n想問全世界係咪只有中國人先鍾意喺公眾地方較到手機個speaker大一大"},{"pid":"967759746d6e1c750ce0779d7025d255deb4a43a","tid":2263082,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:05:43.000Z","msg":"播國歌都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b756dad1531ba5fbbf7aa29b922fa755bdd9e6bd","tid":2263082,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"967759746d6e1c750ce0779d7025d255deb4a43a","tid":2263082,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:05:43.000Z","msg":"播國歌都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:06:53.000Z","msg":"音質太差,眨損國歌"},{"pid":"68f68c1912484d1394b9c799e3615c5b9d1e2239","tid":2263082,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:07:27.000Z","msg":"又聽連意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913a94477524b6421d354afe6de02ca46c016acf","tid":2263082,"uid":370061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:08:24.000Z","msg":"唯一德政"},{"pid":"da2969c7d7826ac3702fffe3ea99457356679bed","tid":2263082,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:09:44.000Z","msg":"無話唔俾清唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}